getmode <- function(v) {
  uniqv <- unique(v)
  uniqv[which.max(tabulate(match(v, uniqv)))]
}
#message("")

pailiangfactor<-function(pailiangfct){
  for(i in c(1:nrow(pailiangfct))){
    if(pailiangfct$pl[1,i]<1) pailiangfct$jc[i]=""
    else if (pailiangfct$pl[1,i]<1.6) pailiangfct$jc[i]=""
    else if (pailiangfct$pl[1,i]<2.5) pailiangfct$jc[i]=""
    else if (pailiangfct$pl[1,i]<4.0) pailiangfct$jc[i]=""
    else if (pailiangfct$pl[1,i]>=4.0) pailiangfct$jc[i]=""
  }
  pailiangfct
}
for(i in c(1:nrow(pailiangfct))){
  if(pailiangfct$`d1$pailiang`[i]<1) pailiangfct$jc[i]=""
  else if (pailiangfct$`d1$pailiang`[i]<1.6) pailiangfct$jc[i]=""
  else if (pailiangfct$`d1$pailiang`[i]<2.5) pailiangfct$jc[i]=""
  else if (pailiangfct$`d1$pailiang`[i]<4.0) pailiangfct$jc[i]=""
  else if (pailiangfct$`d1$pailiang`[i]>=4.0) pailiangfct$jc[i]=""
}

## [1] 12528    36
func<-function(a,cxname){
  myvars <- c("","SUV","","")
  chexing<-a[myvars]
  logbaozhilv <- as.data.frame(log(a$baojia/(a$yuanjia-a$baojia)))
  dim(chexing)
  dim(logbaozhilv)
  #chexing<-merge(chexing, rep("",time=nrow(chexing)))
  chexing$logbaozhilv<-logbaozhilv
  #nrow(chexing)
  #cx<-list(rep("",time=nrow(chexing)))
  cx <- rep("",time=nrow(chexing))
  #dim(cx) <- c(nrow(chexing),1)
  chexing$cx<-cx
  for(i in c(1:nrow(chexing))){
    if(chexing[i,"SUV"]==1)
      chexing[i,ncol(chexing)]="SUV"
    else if(chexing[i,""]==1)
      chexing[i,ncol(chexing)]=""
    else if(chexing[i,""]==1)
      chexing[i,ncol(chexing)]=""
    else
      chexing[i,ncol(chexing)]=""
  }
  names<-c("cx","logbaozhilv")
  chexing<-chexing[names]
  logbaozhilv<-as.numeric(unlist(chexing$logbaozhilv))
  mode(logbaozhilv)
  dataset1 <- data.frame(value = logbaozhilv, group = factor(chexing$cx))
  dataset1
  plotname<-paste('Log',cxname)
  graph<-boxplot(value ~ group,main=plotname,col="yellow",ylab="Log",dataset1)
  graph
}

a<-subset(d1,==1)
